title: Questor (2011) (Alice)cbz
description:
Greece awaits with the greatest of adventures and the most harrowing of heroes! Welcome to a new world of Troy... Idomeneus and Aeson are Questors. Sung by Homer and passed into legend with the taking of Troy, they grew tired of war and the Gods and decided to serve Achaean justice by becoming the finest investigators in the Greek world. When a mysterious woman offers them a case that might put them in opposition to Gods and Titans the question is asked: can a hero ever live up the legend?

enjoy
